            <strong><%= isUk ? 'Compatibility tools' : 'Compatibility tools' %></strong>
            <span class="compatibility-shell__caption"><%= isUk ? 'Legacy mapping, subject visibility, campus routing і migration лишаються тут тільки як advanced bridge/debug layer. Primary setup flow іде через presets, contexts, semesters і live offerings.' : 'Legacy mapping, subject visibility, campus routing, and migration stay here only as an advanced bridge/debug layer. The primary setup flow goes through presets, contexts, semesters, and live offerings.' %></span>
